    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Lava children are ill-tempered creatures created by shaitan genies. Shaped like stunted humanoids with the hideous heads of fanged infants, they prefer to reside in volcanoes. Typical lava children are 5 feet tall and 450 pounds."
        }
    ],
